simple description of functions

bootstrap
 generate and install bootstrap
cean
 manipulate cean working directories, and i/o on /pub repository
cross
 handle cross compilation
devel
 work with local changes of packages
export
 export packages builds into /pub (sources, tarball, packages, installers...)
import
 import packages sources into /src
package
 handle packages, from fetching to build, and install on current bootstrap
rcs
 support rcs for interractive prompt (git svn darcs mercurial monotone...)
test
 manage unit tests and packages status
